## Kill Timeline

**Kill fast**: If kill signal triggered, kill within 2 weeks.

**Rationale**: Wasting resources on bad bets prevents investing in good bets. Kill fast to free resources for higher-value opportunities.

## Quality Gate

- Kill/greenlight criteria must be checked before validation
- Kill/greenlight criteria must be checked before engineering
- Kill decisions must be made within 2 weeks of kill signal
- Greenlight decisions must be documented

**Critical Rule**: No product enters validation or engineering without passing kill/greenlight criteria. Kill fast to avoid wasting resources on bad bets.
